  "<mainText>PASSIVE: +@PassiveArmor@ Armor<br> <br>ACTIVE: Rammus powers himself up and leaps to the largest group of nearby enemies, dealing <scaleArmor>@TotalDamage@</scaleArmor> magic damage (@PercentArmor*100@% Armor %i:scaleArmor% + @ModifiedBonusDamage@), knocking them up for @StunDuration@ seconds, and reducing their Attack Damage %i:scaleAD% by @ADreduction@% for @ADReductionDuration@ seconds.</mainText>": 1,
